                <td>
                    Diagnosis, monitoring and management of congenital adrenal hyperplasia.
                    <br />
                    It is included in neonatal screening programmes.
                    <br />
                    In mildly affected patients, measurement after adrenal stimulation with 
                    Synacthen may be required to confirm the diagnosis.
                </td>
